<Layout title="CPF OA, SA, MA Explained: How Your Contributions Are Split | SalaryCalculator.sg" description="Detailed guide to CPF account types - Ordinary Account, Special Account, and MediSave Account. Learn how contributions are allocated by age and what each account is used for.">
